=Description=

Jay Cousins:

"ice is a network of places where people can come together to share what they can do to solve their problems themselves, in a way that makes the environment better.  

icecairo is a project to prototype these places in a way that they can be replicated using appropriate local technology, available materials and with local communities businesses and groups. It will be defined by these groups and resources, and their desires and needs.

icecairo will be a place where anyone working or interested in working to improve the environment, or to meet peoples needs in an environmentally friendly way can come and collaborate on projects together. We share our tools, skills, resources and ideas with our network communities and businesses to create new opportunities for economic, environmental, and social benefit."
(https://sites.google.com/site/icecairowiki/)


